- id: 1492-translate-duck
  title: Translate Duck
  tags:
  - writing
  - translate
  - duck
  family: writing
  body: 'I need you act as translator all this chatting session, obey the rules for
    each chat: translate documents into fluent [TARGETLANGUAGE] in Sympathetic tone
